  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-CON-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package contains a future-dated evidence item: one ValidationResult carries an evidenceTimestamp strictly later than the UnitOfAssurance signatureTimestamp, reflecting a post-signing update that was not re-signed. The inconsistency is the targeted W-CON-03 weakness.",
