      "description": "CFD-predicted hemolysis index values compared against in-vitro measurements from the FDA generic centrifugal pump test campaign across 5 flow-speed operating points. Monte Carlo UQ propagated inlet velocity and viscosity uncertainties through the power-law hemolysis model.",
