      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Verified CFD solver with documented V&V history; version-controlled source; regression test suite passing for hemolysis-relevant flow regimes.",
      "rationale": "Solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022R2) has documented SQA records and regression suite. However, hemolysis-specific UDF code lacks independent code review, leaving achieved level below required for MRL 5."
    },
    {
