      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation geometry, flow regime, and operating conditions match COU VAD device within documented similarity criteria.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic pump (open-source geometry). COU device is a proprietary centrifugal VAD with different impeller blade angle and tip clearance. Geometric similarity index computed at 0.71, below the 0.85 threshold required for MRL 5."
    },
