      "rationale": "No independent analyst review performed. Single analyst conducted all simulation setup and post-processing. Use error factor not formally assessed; treated as epistemic gap."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model and hemolysis constitutive model selection justified by sensitivity study and literature evidence for VAD-relevant flow regimes.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected without sensitivity comparison to RSM or LES. Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen) used without comparison to Bludszuweit or Arora models. Model form uncertainty not quantified at MRL 5 level."
